  </a>
  <a href="https://ipa-name-training-karuta.pages.dev/cards_ipa-vs-name.html" target="_blank" class="card">
    <img src="img/5_symbol_name.png">
    <div class="title">⑤<br>一覧表<br>記号 → 名称</div>
  </a>
  <a href="https://ipa-name-training-karuta.pages.dev/cards.html" target="_blank" class="card">
    <img src="img/6_word_symbol.png">
    <div class="title">⑥<br>一覧表<br>例単語 → 名称＋記号</div>
  </a>
  <a href="https://ipa-name-training-karuta.pages.dev/cards_name-vs-examples.html" target="_blank" class="card">
