  </a>
  <a href="https://ipa-name-training-karuta.pages.dev/cards_ipa-vs-examples.html" target="_blank" class="card">
    <img src="img/8_symbol_word.png">
    <div class="title">⑧<br>一覧表<br>記号 → 例単語</div>
  </a>
  <a href="https://ipa-name-training-karuta.pages.dev/cards_examples-vs-ipa.html" target="_blank" class="card">
